title: Watch: These people actually let Jimmy Fallon see their Google search history
text:
Well not Fallon exactly, but someone from The Tonight Show who then passed all their Google searches onto him to broadcast to the world.
Sound. To be fair, they're lucky they got such PC results. And is it just us or is that Bill Hader at the 1:30 mark?
Via YouTube
